{"tid":350904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵成立高級別檢討委員會　調查觀塘線事故","createTime":"2017-08-07T14:58:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T15:49:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"76040e67caf7e73df46cb5b6af0f42e68a5a8846","tid":350904,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170807/s00001/6194bbf30186b25d57aa3c90416008ba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170807%2Fs00001%2F6194bbf30186b25d57aa3c90416008ba.jpg&h=d282114b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港鐵觀塘線上周六（5日）早上11時許發生信號故障，列車服務受阻逾10小時。港鐵今表示，將成立高級別檢討委員會，調查觀塘線事故。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵今表示，已成立一個高級別檢討委員會，全方位審視今次事故的成因及處理程序，並找出可作改善之處。港鐵已委任車務及中國內地業務常務總監金澤培為委員會主席，委員會其他成員包括來自公司的車務處及技術工程處的資深員工。港鐵亦會聘任獨立專家顧問，向委員會就事故原因及處理程序的檢討提供專業意見。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵行政總裁梁國權表示，港鐵公司非常重視這次事件，「對於是次事故對乘客造成不便，我們表示歉意」，亦感謝乘客的體諒和配合。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指出，委員會將就不同範疇進行全面檢討，包括事故的起因、事故應變和恢復服務安排的適時性和有效性，預計約兩個月內向政府提交初步的檢討結果。"},{"pid":"1ef3efeb41329b64d9d14051cbb8d214a10bd197","tid":350904,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:58:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170807/s00001/1502113816514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170807%2Fs00001%2F1502113816514&d=IJJG6Fkgf%2B7LG2uSGTY3T10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=47e0284a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170807%2Fs00001%2F1502113816514&h=97aa31d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170807/s00001/1502113816514</a>"},{"pid":"67f98350d33123ada78f1f9c1598ab435f5c3c2b","tid":350904,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:59:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b0283cfc6cee5ab257f927443c250887c6a8d17","tid":350904,"uid":129111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"自己査自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f74701bcb73d95ddf25b05fa1311a6a066ac30","tid":350904,"uid":130513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T15:04:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8ccc9802f0be791c1d6879b01b9cfa24fc72db6b","tid":350904,"uid":36178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T15:05:54.000Z","msg":"「高級」「別調查」"},{"pid":"56720cc3db36ab6a826ebc969f8dca66af21aa8f","tid":350904,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T15:10:44.000Z","msg":"調查完決定加價提高服務"},{"pid":"5c208d94ff4e201a6126c330828ad08710cf66e8","tid":350904,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T07:27:27.000Z","msg":"乘機引入蝗蟲，開會要用匪語"},{"pid":"6e604a6d250e0119c3ff16c089e935358d44f33e","tid":350904,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}